  <p>The Infrastructure and Services pattern should be used to showcase a service or product and link to it's page for more information if there is one. Infrastructure and Services is not the same thing as a value prop and should not be used as one. This should summarize a product or service that we offer in an approachable and not overly technical way.  </p>
